hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: A company car kamagra rezeptfrei aus deutschland smartphone innovation? How about making the screen out of something OTHER than glass. What is it, 1922? We have had poly-carb and shatter-proof materials in common eye-glasses now for over 50 years. Yet this stumps the ‘tech geniuses’ who are worried more about the next boring iteration of angry birds instead of making a phone that lasts more than 3 months. -Sent from my broken stupid little iPhone :)
